{"tid":1538920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肛狗同謝狗今日個樣淆撚到","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:06.000Z","uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"81bb861791b7fab593c7912baf0c434e53aa0e40","tid":1538920,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc2c85dd96b8941855308e4fa29383c7c8247f0","tid":1538920,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081603353aacba0a1ba10e0e1f17ec4db213d4f0","tid":1538920,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51feac2b57463e522d7ef12298337ea0a32f6dfd","tid":1538920,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28f3c1c62b986f9ee31ef63099634826836f388","tid":1538920,"uid":93649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"Er蛇琴日仲叫大家拭目以待<br />\n原來係咁解"},{"pid":"438b128b8f596af3758855308439dad5bb0ef79b","tid":1538920,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"3ec0379bffc5a555c0c84744dec4d84ac48c726d","tid":1538920,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:06.000Z","msg":"警察將被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}